Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1314.jpg'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'Upper Level, Competition Zone', 2: 'Everett Arena'}
{3: 'Everett Arena\\nUpper Level, Competition Zone'}
{3: 'Night has fallen, yet the arena remains packed to the brim, with blinding lights and deafening music assaulting the senses of every spectator.'}
{3: "Humans throughout the crowd buzz with excitement, eagerly awaiting the day's first mechanoid death match."}
{3: 'Countless eyes fixed on the arena center betray barely contained excitement, all desperate for the mechanoid combat to begin.'}
{3: 'They crave the sight of mechanoid parts shattering and vital fluid pooling across the ground—this ultimate form of "entertainment" is what they desire.'}
{3: "Pulsing electronic sounds blare from speakers throughout the arena, heralding the fierce combat that's about to begin."}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiLivWarmActivity/FxUiLivWarmActivityVinylBo.prefab', 2: '3'}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: 'Ladies and gentlemen, welcome to the Everett Arena! A new round of mechanoid combat for this season is about to begin!'}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: 'As with previous seasons, winners advance to the next round, while the losers will, unfortunately, be eliminated.'}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: "And this season's champion will receive our grand prize—and that, lo and behold, is FREEDOM!!"}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: 'The victorious mechanoid gladiator will be able to leave this place and start their life anew!'}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: 'And those who bet on this lucky gladiator will also receive massive payouts from our prize pool!'}
{2: 'Virtual Host', 3: 'So sit back and enjoy this ultimate entertainment, and have a wonderful evening, everyone!'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiLivWarmActivity/FxUiLivWarmActivityVinylBo.prefab'}
{1: '999', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory428.jpg', 3: '0', 4: '0.1', 5: '0.2'}

{3: "As the virtual host's introduction concludes, intense spotlights jump to life simultaneously, their beams converging on the arena's center to illuminate a mechanism activating in the floor. A massive octagonal iron cage slowly rises from below."}
{3: "As people see clearly what's inside the cage, they erupt into wild cheers."}
{1: '999', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory428.jpg', 3: '0.1', 4: '0', 5: '0.2'}

{1: '1', 3: 'Inside is a bizarre mechanical monstrosity reminiscent of a long-tailed mechanical spider that flexes its limbs within the cage, its joints grinding together with an ear-piercing screech.'}
{3: 'Seemingly sensing the human audience\'s cheers, the mechanical spider lets out a deafening roar from its vocal module, as though impatiently urging its "prey" to enter the battlefield.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgCg/Cg5901_13.jpg'}

{3: 'With the echoing screech, an iron gate on one side of the arena thunderously slides open. Measured footsteps can be heard from the dim corridor, accompanied by the scrape of a weapon being dragged across the metal floor.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiStoryBlackPassScene.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1314.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator B', 3: "Heard today's fight is gonna be a real thriller. Wonder who's stepping into the ring this time?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator A', 3: "Last week's match wrecked like ten fighters. They definitely need fresh meat today!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Spectator B', 3: "Pfft! This new season's been going for almost three months, and not a single fighter has lived long enough for a second round.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator B', 3: 'They won a match, then immediately got their heads blown off by another gladiator in the next. So damn boring!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator B', 3: 'I bet on a bunch of bruisers last season. Looked tough as hell, but not a single one of those bastards won!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: 'Are you still betting on this one today, then?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Spectator B', 3: "What's the rush? Let's see what happens first! Ain't no way I'm gonna throw my money down the drain again. By the way, how much did you lose last time...?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: "Let's not even go there... Hey, look! The gladiator's coming out!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 3: 'A masked female mechanoid, lance in hand, emerges from the shadowy corridor and steps into the harsh spotlight.'}
{3: 'Unlike the mechanical gladiators from the seasons before with their basic coatings and barely humanoid shapes, her form is almost indistinguishable from that of a human.'}
{3: 'With bizarre-looking "horns" protruding from her hair and a long "tail" trailing behind her, she draws all eyes.'}
{3: "The display screen above the gate flashes with a name the audience doesn't recognize..."}
{3: '"Veronica"'}
{1: 'DialogEnable'}

{1: '1', 3: 'The moment the giant spider sees its opponent enter the battlefield, its programmed "hatred" sends it into a frenzy. Its razor-sharp limbs scratch the metal floor, making a sound that sets everyone\'s teeth on edge.'}
{1: 'RImgBg1Shake'}
{3: 'The mechanical spider rams frantically against its cage, its piercing shrieks echoing throughout every corner of the arena as it tries to shred the mechanoid gladiator outside.'}
{3: 'The moment Veronica enters the battlefield, however, waves of disapproving boos ripple through the stands.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator A', 3: "Tch, that's it?", 4: '1'}

{2: 'Spectator A', 3: "I thought we were promised a brutal combat with fierce mechanoid gladiators! What's so exciting about this scrawny lady?! She ain't got nothing on that bruiser from the other day that crushed ten dudes in a row!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator B', 3: "Word! They talked the talk but ain't walking the walk. Dammit, I want my money back!", 4: '2'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator C', 3: "What are you two whining about? This is where the real show begins! What's so exciting about watching those weird-looking mechanoids blow off one another's heads day after day?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator C', 3: "Look at her—she's so human-like, and with that tail, too. It's fascinating! Never seen a mechanoid like this before.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator C', 3: 'Just imagine when that giant spider tears her apart and devours her bit by bit... Now, that is entertainment!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator C', 3: "You won't see scenes like that in any movie—that's what makes mechanoid combat so damn thrilling!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator B', 3: 'Damn... When you put it that way, it does sound pretty exciting...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator A', 3: "When you explain it like that, it does sound pretty intense! You really know what you're talking about, kid!", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Worked up by these violent fantasies, the spectators leap to their feet and shout toward the center of the arena.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator A', 3: "Hey—what's-your-name—Vero... whatever! You, the metal freak with the tail! You better put up a good fight before you die, got it? Don't waste my ticket money!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: 'I want to see some real action! You hear me?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Hearing this, Veronica slowly turns toward the spectator in the stands.'}
{1: '1', 3: "She removes her mask, revealing a face almost indistinguishable from a human's."}
{3: 'Her mask crashes to the ground with a thunderous clang. Her crimson eyes focus with icy rage, their gaze threatening to pierce right through the disrespectful spectator.'}
{3: 'She raises her massive lance, its tip gleaming with lethal brilliance as she points it directly at the human in the stands.'}
{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'Shut. Your. Mouth.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Perhaps sensing the hostility in her eyes, the spectator falls silent, though the contemptuous glares aimed at her remain.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator A', 3: 'GoDDamn it! Did I just get cowed by a worthless toaster?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Spectator B', 3: "Oho, that's exactly your type, ain't it? Aren't you usually into the feisty ones?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: "What the hell are you talking about?! It's just a piece of junk metal! I don't care what it looks like—you think I'd be into a machine?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: "Cocky little brat. I can't wait to see what she looks like when that massive beast crushes her to pieces...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Spectator B', 3: "For crying out loud, cut us all some slack, will ya? Sit down—I'm trying to record this fight and you're blocking my shot!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Spectator A', 3: '...Tch. This better be worth the damn ticket.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Malice and contempt from the human crowd wash over the arena like a tide, mingled with their insatiable hunger for violence and bloodshed.'}
{3: 'They crave to see mechanoids slaughtered, mutilated, and mercilessly shattered into fragments in the arena.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1204.jpg'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiStoryMovieFilm.prefab', 2: '2'}
{3: 'In the twilight of the Golden Age, this spectacle unfolds under the spotlights night after night—and such is humanity\'s idea of "entertainment."'}
{3: 'Only immersed in such brutality do these human spectators—their senses already dulled by ordinary diversions—find their eyes lighting up with that peculiar gleam.'}
{3: 'Little do these spectators, immersed in their violent entertainment, realize that their own twisted cheers of excitement are simultaneously being "appreciated" as a spectacle themselves.'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiStoryMovieFilm.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStoryFront/BgStoryFront12.png', 4: '4'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1314.jpg'}
{3: '—Unbeknownst to them, a "distinguished guest" silently observes it all from a room above them behind an enormous one-way mirror.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1310.jpg'}
{3: 'Numerous display screens spread out at perfect angles before this "distinguished guest," streaming real-time footage from every corner of the arena in exquisite detail.'}
{3: 'Behind the human "distinguished guest" stands a massive mechanoid, motionless and silent, its metallic shell reflecting the dim glow from the monitors.'}
{3: 'Its sensitive optical recognition system detects the slightest gesture from the human and responds immediately.'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Overseer', 3: 'Master, the room temperature is currently 25°C with 55% relative humidity. I notice your attire today is rather light. Would you like me to adjust the temperature to a more comfortable setting?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The human does not respond.'}
{2: 'Overseer', 3: 'Due to the intense combat in previous seasons, some gladiators would move out of camera range during matches.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Overseer', 3: "To enhance your viewing experience, I've installed additional cameras throughout the arena to ensure you can monitor every aspect of the match in real time.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: "You've always handled these trivial matters well. You're a good butler, indeed. But you should understand what I truly desire.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "I'm tired of watching these mechanical gladiators fighting mechanical beasts. I want something I've never seen.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Overseer', 3: 'Master, this "Veronica" will show you something completely different.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Overseer', 3: 'Based on my predictive analysis of her frame parameters, there\'s a high probability she could be the perfect candidate for your "plan."', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: "Excellent. Let the match begin, then. I can't wait.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Overseer', 3: "Yes, Master. Please enjoy the show. I'll compile the data from this match and provide you with a detailed analysis afterward.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The massive mechanoid withdraws at its "Master\'s" command, and silence returns to the room.'}
{3: 'The "Master" turns back to the display screens that capture every detail of the arena.'}
{3: 'At this moment, every screen focuses on "Veronica", who is about to face her very first arena battle.'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Surprise me... "Veronica".', 4: '1'}
{1: '—PERFECT CAGE—', 2: 'ER14', 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Atlas/CommonLogo/BgLogo1.png'}
{1: 'ThemeEnable'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Ui/Spine/3-8Spine/UiMovieWeiluonikaV38/UiMovieWeiluonikaV38.prefab'}
{3: 'With the buzzer signaling the start of the match, the cage holding the mechanical giant spider unlocks, its heavy iron bars slamming to the ground.'}
{3: 'The freed mechanical spider lets out a piercing shriek as it leaps forward and launches itself toward the mechanical gladiator.'}
{3: 'Meanwhile, massive screens above the arena flicker to life, capturing every angle of the battleground for countless spectators to see.'}
{3: 'Thunderous cheers erupt from the stands and sweep through every corner of the arena with stifling heat.'}
{3: 'The mechanical spider looms over the gladiator, dwarfing her tall frame beneath its massive bulk.'}
{3: 'Veronica grips her lance tightly as she readies herself, poised to thrust at her opponent at any moment.'}
{3: 'In the giant spider\'s programming, such defiance triggers its "rage" protocol. It lashes its barbed tail like a whip at Veronica.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '3'}
{3: "But Veronica quickly sidesteps the attack, causing the spider's massive tail to crash into the ground and kick up a cloud of dust."}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1314.jpg'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineFocusNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Enraged by the failed attack, the mechanical spider whirls around and slashes its razor-sharp limbs as it lunges at Veronica once more.'}
{3: 'This unexpected turn drives the crowd into a frenzy, their screams growing even more frantic.'}
{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'This pointless game of slaughter...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'What a waste of my time.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineFocusNew.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStoryFront/BgStoryFront12.png', 4: '5'}
{1: 'DialogEnable'}
{1: '1', 3: "Veronica's crimson eyes blaze with rage as she fearlessly stares down the mechanical spider towering over her."}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '3'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineSpreadNew.prefab', 2: '2', 5: '1'}
{3: "In that moment, she unleashes the energy stored within her frame and launches herself skyward with her lance pointed at the mechanical spider's core."}
{3: 'As she soars above the giant spider, time seems to stand still in the arena. All eyes are on her now.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1314.jpg', 2: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiHit01.prefab', 2: '3'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineSpreadNew.prefab', 5: '1'}
{3: 'She twirls her lance and drives it down with deadly precision.'}
